In this screenshot, you can see a document editing program, including buttons for setting text alignment. To select the center alignment button, you need to move the mouse over the button and click it.
The following is the JSON format representation of specific steps:```json
[
    {"action_type": "MouseAction", "mouse_action_type": "click", "mouse_button": "left", "mouse_position": {"width": 912, "height": 144}}
]
```
